---
layout: base
title: Seasonal
description: What's in season now, and which recipes will make the most of it.
permalink: /seasonal/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-20);">

  <header class="recipe-hero">
    <span class="recipe-hero__eyebrow">Cook with the calendar</span>
    <h1 class="recipe-hero__title">Seasonal</h1>
    <p class="recipe-hero__dek">What is at the farmers market right now, and which of our recipes will make the most of it.</p>
  </header>

  {% set allRecipes = collections.recipes | reverse %}
  {% if allRecipes.length > 0 %}
  <section style="margin-top: var(--space-8);">
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-headline); font-size: var(--text-xl); margin: 0 0 var(--space-4); padding-bottom: var(--space-3); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-accent);">All recipes</h2>
    <div class="recipe-grid">
      {% for recipe in allRecipes %}
        {% set recipe = recipe %}
        {% include "partials/recipe-card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% else %}
  <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--text-md); color: var(--color-ink-faint);">No recipes published yet.</p>
  {% endif %}

</div>
